{
  "texts": [
    "As AI methodologies advance, there's a growing expectation that these tools will be applied to lesser-studied targets.",
    "While these studies have yielded successful results, the molecules generated do not show significant structural or binding mode differences compared to known ligands.",
    "Consequently, de novo techniques have shown more success in drug optimization rather than in the discovery of entirely novel hits.",
    "In 2021, Yu et al.",
    "(22) undertook a scaffold hopping campaign to identify novel structures for JAK1 inhibition."
  ]
}